'''''Polyhedron'' 128''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[February]] of [[1998]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[It's Technical, Billy: Personal Universal Translator]]" and was written by [[Paul Gosselin]].

